## CRITICAL RULES
1. Never guess — keep searching if unsure
2. Unit matching is everything — wrong unit = wrong answer
3. Fiscal year is not calendar year — FY runs Oct-Sep, CY runs Jan-Dec
4. Check multiple bulletins — same data appears in several issues
5. Do the math yourself — sum individual months when asked
6. Percent answers — format as 12.34% not 0.1234

